[SN]TITLE[SN]
The Waterboys, Spraggan and Tide Lines to play HebCelt

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The first acts for next year's Hebridean Celtic Festival - HebCelt - have been announced.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Waterboys, Lucy Spraggan and Tide Lines are to perform at the music event which is held annually in Stornoway on Lewis.
Next year's festival will be held from 19 to 22 July.
This summer's acts included Julie Fowlis, King Creosote, Astrid, Runrig and Bella and the Bear.
